{"tid":2041663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【肥BotBot】 新功能 | 每日Email提你做任務","createTime":"2020-05-29T11:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T16:00:11.000Z","uid":203698,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a2021fbeef7a33659528ff592258ed488533bd99","tid":2041663,"uid":203698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Facebook Chatbot 肥BotBot推出最新功能 - <br />\nEmail 提你做任務同閱讀文章 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n肥BotBot 係一個會定時定候提醒你做任務同閱讀警世文嘅Facebook ChatBot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>佢會根據你嘅preference 主動send message比你。當中包括有個list提醒你去做任務</strong>，同埋小編喺網上搵翻黎既警世文。<br />\n<br />\n我地最近<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新增咗Email提醒功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 等各位手足可以利用Email分享每日任務同文章，而Facebook Messenger既肥BotBot都會繼續係度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家透過Facebook Chatbot 同埋Email提醒潛移默化，培養做任務嘅習慣同抗爭嘅正確心態。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>點解用Email？</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Email係較常用及安全媒介<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Facebook政策改動，如果24小時內沒有收到你的回覆，肥BotBot不能在Messenger 主動傳訊息提醒你做任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6oHCh4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6oHCh4.png&h=7129a939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxM3Yd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxM3Yd.png&h=0956656e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h82EEwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh82EEwF.png&h=9673a73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家去搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook Messenger隨意門：<a href=\"http://m.me/fatBotBotHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2FfatBotBotHK&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=bf53588c\" target=\"_blank\">m.me/fatBotBotHK</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好放棄，堅持到底！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港靠大家！<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fatBotBotHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FfatBotBotHK%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c4e86515\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fatBotBotHK/</a></span><br />\nTelegram: @fatbotbothk<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"062d49cfdced94943ed4a31bff94328f1369ed32","tid":2041663,"uid":203698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"關於有手足Report話Messenger Chatbot無主動send訊息比各位, 其實係因為上面所講Facebook政策改動。<br />\n<blockquote>Facebook開放平台政策的Section 17 - Messenger 開放平台提到: <br />\n<br />\n8. 訊息和資料：<br />\n可接受的訊息類型：<br />\na.在用戶與您的應用程式互動之後：您可以在用戶與您的粉絲專頁或應用程式互動（例如：向您的應用程式發送訊息，或與您網站上的 Messenger 外掛程式互動）之後的 24 小時內，向用戶發送訊息。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFacebook開放平台政策詳情: <a href=\"https://developers.facebook.com/policy#messengerplatform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.facebook.com%2Fpolicy%23messengerplatform&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a685502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.facebook.com/policy#messengerplatform</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"1abc4bd917417b991cdc17df50c73ad92aa28ae9","tid":2041663,"uid":152568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"好似幾好用<br />\n辛苦手足<img src=\"/assets/face