/span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"062d49cfdced94943ed4a31bff94328f1369ed32","tid":2041663,"uid":203698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"關於有手足Report話Messenger Chatbot無主動send訊息比各位, 其實係因為上面所講Facebook政策改動。<br />\n<blockquote>Facebook開放平台政策的Section 17 - Messenger 開放平台提到: <br />\n<br />\n8. 訊息和資料：<br />\n可接受的訊息類型：<br />\na.在用戶與您的應用程式互動之後：您可以在用戶與您的粉絲專頁或應用程式互動（例如：向您的應用程式發送訊息，或與您網站上的 Messenger 外掛程式互動）之後的 24 小時內，向用戶發送訊息。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFacebook開放平台政策詳情: <a href=\"https://developers.facebook.com/policy#messengerplatform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.facebook.com%2Fpolicy%23messengerplatform&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a685502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.facebook.com/policy#messengerplatform</a>[/quote]"}}